project.title: Integrity AI
project.description: Welcome to IntegrityAI where you can find trusted partners in the passive crypto space. We are people of integrity that have experienced the “rug pulls” in this space and wanted to come up with something ourselves in order to provide a REAL revenue source for you to be able to plug into. Many of you KNOW the people behind this project, but we can’t tell you, in order that we can maintain our anonymity to provide you with this very great opportunity. Every trading platform has risk. So, we do not intend to promise you that this is without that. But we promise to do everything we can to offset that risk with the best risk management we can muster. After all, with legit trading, we don’t win if you lose! We look forward to standing the test of time and going beyond that 6–9-month death sentence that seems to be getting shorter with all these opportunists coming on the scene. We are doing real trading. We hope that those who choose to be “risk takers” and take us at face value will do so to get started, and those who are the more cautious ones will take all the time they need to “watch and see” as their friends stay winning with IntegrityAI.
